<div class="wrapper wrapper_padding clearfix">
  <div class="col-1 about homepage_content">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <hr>
    <p>Part time Web Developer</p>
    <p>I am amazed at the simplicity and usability of Ruby and Rails. What started as a curiosity in Rails soon got me building small websites. Checkout some of the projects I have built. The source code is on <a href="https://github.com/sundars04?tab=repositories" target="_blank">Github</a>.</p>
    <p>You can find me sharing some code on Github.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-2 homepage_content">
    <h2>Stuff I've Written</h2>
    <hr>
    <% @posts.each do |post| %>
      <h3><a href="#"><%= link_to post.title, post %></a></h3>
      <p class="date"><%= post.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-3 homepage_content">
    <h2>Stuff I've Built</h2>
    <hr>
    <% @projects.each do |project| %>
      <h3><a href="#"><%= link_to project.title, project %></a></h3>
      <p class="date"><%= project.created_at.strftime("%A, %b %d") %></p>
    <% end %>
    
  </div>
</div>